SELECT authorised_value,lib FROM authorised_values WHERE category='Bsort2'

elements.description: L'adhrent class par -15 ans / 15-65 ans / +65 ans
elements.expression: CASE WHEN FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-12-31'),iuqi)/365)<15 THEN '0  15 ans Enfants'           WHEN FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-12-31'),iuqi)/365)<65 THEN '15  65 ans'           WHEN iuqi IS NULL OR iuqi='' THEN 'Inconnu'  ELSE '65 ans et +' END
elements.viewExpression: CASE WHEN FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-12-31'),#iuqi)/365)<15 THEN '0  15 ans Enfants'           WHEN FLOOR(DATEDIFF(CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-12-31'),#iuqi)/365)<65 THEN '15  65 ans'           WHEN #iuqi IS NULL OR #iuqi='' THEN 'Inconnu'  ELSE '65 ans et +' END

elements.expression: agas IN ('issue','renew') AND DATE(acoh) BETWEEN CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-01-01') AND CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-12-31')
elements.viewExpression: #agas IN ('issue','renew') AND DATE(#acoh) BETWEEN CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-01-01') AND CONCAT(YEAR(NOW())-1,'-12-31')
